  "description": "This dataset comprises laser-evoked potentials recorded simultaneously from the human spinal cord and cortex. The study investigates nociceptive processing across multiple levels of the somatosensory system using high-resolution electrophysiological recordings. Data were collected to characterize the spatiotemporal dynamics of pain-related neural responses in both spinal and cortical structures.",
